    "Bing more often mislabeled statements attributed to Russian officials for Ukrainian prompts (63%), Russian users for English prompts (24%), and statements with no source for Russian prompts (50%).",
    "Regression analysis resultsTo test the effect of various factors on the performance of chatbots for veracity detection, we performed three regression analyses (Figs. 7, 8 and 9).",
    "First, we examined factors influencing labeling of the accuracy variable.",
    "Figure 7 demonstrates that there are no statistically significant factors influencing the incorrect assessment of whether the statement is true, false or partially true.",
